iaik.pkcs.pkcs11.wrapper

Interface PKCS11Constants


  • public interface PKCS11Constants
    This interface holds constants of the PKCS#11 v2.11 standard. This is mainly the content of the 'pkcs11t.h' header file. Mapping of primitiv data types to Java types:
